public int getTileOfNextCluster()
Return the tile of the NEXT ILLUMINA_DATA object to be returned by the method next. This might force us to advance to the next file (as it will contains the data for the next) tile/ILLUMINA_DATA object.

verifyData

public void verifyData(java.util.List<java.lang.Integer> tiles,
                       int[] cycles)
Given the expected tiles and cycles for this run, make sure this parser can provide data for all tiles/cycles or throws an exception if it's missing any required data or data structures it relies on do not disagree with the provided tiles/cycles

Parameters:
tiles - The number of tiles in the current run
cycles - The number of cycles in the current run
